### GET all items
GET http://localhost:3000/api/items

### GET one item
GET http://localhost:3000/api/items/1

### GET missing item (404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/items/999

### CREATE an item (201)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Buy milk",
  "status": "todo"
}

### CREATE with missing name (400 validation)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "todo"
}

### UPDATE an item (200)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/items/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "done"
}

### DELETE an item (200)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/items/2
